Name: Airborn
About the game: VR was made for this, you were born for this Soar through the air and decimate their fleet. Fight off a never-ending onslaught of robotic enemies by combining devastating firepower and unparalleled mobility. An intuitive physical control scheme lets you pull off incredible aerial maneuvers at breakneck speed, while still keeping the experience comfortable for VR-sickness sufferers. Unparallelled Mobility No more standing around. Take to the skies to get the drop on your enemies, with a physical control scheme that prevents motion sickness. You've never moved in VR like this. A worthy challenge Your enemies are monstrous, and many. Keep your wits about you as you weave between agile drones and colossal war machines. Become the ultimate weapon Unlock perks and customize your loadout to exceed your limitations. Complete missions, earn experience, and craft your perfect build. They won't know what hit them.
